<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5093180>
    dc:description "Figs 1, 2. Bohemannia auriciliella (DE JOANNIS,1909). 1. Female, Hannover,13. June 2018,TLMF Lep 25991 (Photo:TINA SCHULZ). 2. Male,Netherlands, Noord-Brabant,Riethoven, 26 June 2015, RMNH. INS.25160.SCale bar 1mm (Photo: ERIK VAN NIEUKERKEN)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5093180/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5093182>
    dc:description "Fig. 3. Male genitalia of Bohemannia auriciliella (DE JOANNIS, 1909).3a. Ventral vieW. 3b. FoCussed more dorsally.Genitalia slide EvN5160, RMNH.INS.25160. SCale bars 100μm (Photo:ERIK VAN NIEUKERKEN)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5093182/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5093184>
    dc:description "Fig. 4. Female genitalia of Bohemannia auriciliella (DE JOAN- NIS,1909), Holotype. Only the terminal segments are illustrated, as the bursa did not shoW any detail. 4a. Dorsal vieW. 4b. FoCussed more ventrally.Genitalia slide KL0720 (Photo: ERIK VAN NIEUKERKEN)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5093184/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

